      <title>日本央行加剧波动 瑞穗银行寻求内部资深日本国债分析师</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/mizuho-seeks-in-house-jgb-veterans-as-boj-moves-fuel-volatility</link>
